experience.description:
Full cycle of managing the IT recruitment projects for Russian and international
companies:

- Communicating with customers to determine technical requirements and
work specifics;
- Sourcing candidates using different tools, like hh.ru, Linkedin, Habr,
AmazingHiring, Telegram, Github, etc.
- Screening candidates for competency with the job requirements;
- Optimize the recruitment process by negotiating with hiring managers and HR managers;
- Interviewing candidates and writing expert comments;
- Job descriptions writing and posting (HH, Linkedin, Hays website, etc.);
- Participation in internal PR - activities to increase brand exposure Preparing;
- IT market research (salary guides or market mapping). 

Project examples : Backend developers (Python, Golang, C++ .NET), DevOps engineers, Project managers, Product managers, Product designers, UX researchers, SAP implementation consultants (FI, CO, MM, SD, HCM), Abap Developers, Anaplan Model Builders.

Achievements:
- Stable annual sales plan fulfilment 
-  High HPI (candidate and customer satisfaction rate of 9.31 out of 10)
- Growth from Associate to Consultant (3 steps).
- Effective work with personal associate - training intern from scratch, almost full delegation function of searching.
- Regular support of new employees as Buddy


*Due to the geopolitical situation, the headquarters in London decided to suspend the company's business in Russia. Till March  2022 the company is separated from Hays Worldwide and continues to provide services with the brand Getexperts.
